title: What Font is this? It's at the back of my head!
content:
Hi guys!  
I know i somehow know this font... but i'm not sure what it is.  
The spur of the letter G is similar to Frutiger but Frutiger isn't as robust looking.

Any quick answers?  
Thanks!  
Patrick
